title: Experts warn White House's budget cuts could make tsunami warnings less reliable
description: In Alaska, a federal grant that funded seismic data collection in order to warn people about tsunamis is being cancelled. Experts say cuts like this could make tsunami warnings less reliable.
content: In Alaska, a federal grant that funded seismic data collection in order to warn people about tsunamis is being cancelled. Experts say cuts like this could make tsunami warnings less reliable.
de: Experten warnen davor, dass die Haushaltskürzungen des Weißen Hauses die Zuverlässigkeit der Tsunami-Warnungen beeinträchtigen könnten. In Alaska wird ein Bundeszuschuss zur Finanzierung der seismischen Datenerfassung zur Warnung der Menschen vor Tsunamis gestrichen. Experten gehen davon aus, dass solche Kürzungen dazu führen könnten, dass Tsunami-Warnungen weniger zuverlässig sind.
en: Experts warn White House's budget cuts could make tsunami warnings less reliable. In Alaska, a federal grant that funded seismic data collection in order to warn people about tsunamis is being cancelled. Experts say cuts like this could make tsunami warnings less reliable.
la: Periti monent fiscalitatem fiscalem albam incisis facere posse tsunami monita minus certa. In Alaska, da foederati ut collectio seismica fundis data sit ut homines de tsunamis cassantur moneant. Periti dicunt secat simile hoc tsunami monita minus certa facere potuisse.
